widgets.label: Send
widgets.onValue:
if(get("module_switch") === "Broadcast"){
send("localhost:5000","broadcast",get("OSC_message"))
}
else
{
let args = get("OSC_message").split(' ')

switch (args.length) {
  case 1: 
console.log("sending " + args[0] + " to " + get("OSC_address"))
    send("localhost:4000",get("OSC_address"),Number(args[0]))
    break
  case 2: 
    send("localhost:4000",get("OSC_address"),Number(args[0]),Number(args[1]))
    break
  case 3: 
    send("localhost:4000",get("OSC_address"),Number(args[0]),Number(args[1]),Number(args[2]))
    break
  case 4: 
    send("localhost:4000",get("OSC_address"),Number(args[0]),Number(args[1]),Number(args[2]),Number(args[3]))
    break
  default:
    break
  }
}
